======================== Set Up =====================================
sudo apt update
sudo apt install python3-tk
sudo apt install ffmpeg             // for ffmpeg - pydub
python3 -m venv v_environment
source v_environment/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

export PS1="\u@\h:\W\$ "   // pentru scurtarea terminalului


======================== Warning ====================================
cuvintele de TIP: "word[word]" -> cum_se_aude[cum_se_subintelege]
... - may mean word dublication like - eu am... am fost

